Coffee syrup.
A kilo of coffee is burned, ground and yes
he puts it in a painted earthenware pot, pours it
above 2 liters of boiling water, it is well diluted with
a spatula, close it hermetically and leave it
for one day in a rather warm place.

Then you pass it to the filter. To every part of this
fusion, two of virgin syrup are added:
then it is placed over a gentle heat and left to simmer for a long time
reached 32 degrees.
